OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA fine and largely sunny day,
OL,6,Fwith any overnight cloud soon
OL,7,Fclearing. Warm sunshine gradually
OL,8,Fturning hazy through the afternoon as
OL,9,Fhigh cloud thickens from the north,
OL,10,Fbut staying dry. Best of the sunshine
OL,11,Facross southern parts. Light winds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FDry evening with some clearer
OL,14,Fspells, mainly in the south. A band of
OL,15,Fthicker cloud will spread south
OL,16,Fovernight, perhaps with brief light
OL,17,Frain but likely staying dry.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
