OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FEarly cloud will break to
OL,6,Fsunny spells, before further cloud
OL,7,Fspreads south through the morning,
OL,8,Fperhaps bringing a few showers. Most
OL,9,Fparts staying dry and warm. Breezy.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FSunny
OL,12,Fspells and showers Sunday, these
OL,13,Fperhaps heavy at times. Drier Monday,
OL,14,Fwith variable cloud and sunny spells.
OL,15,FCloudier and breezier Tuesday, with
OL,16,Frain across hills. Temperatures near
OL,17,Fnormal.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
